title: FS2004 - Samsoft - Taiwan Today 2005
description:
Taiwan Today 2005, a great enhancement of the default FS2004 Taiwan scenery, and much improvement from previous version. it includes not only the three great airports but also the cities. It enhances the Chiang Kai Shek International airport, Sung Shan airport and Kaoshiung International Airport. It also includes moving cars. Plus the cities of Taipei, Keelung and Kaoshiung are much enhanced, as well as the city textures. 
Eur15.95 for new buyers; USD9.95 for previous version buyers and it needs the previous version password to setup (go to order page) 

Features of this product: 
?CKS airport with custom design 
?Realistic terminal buildings 
?Realistic tower 
?taxing lines 
?Added trees around the airport 
?Added buildings and some Taiwan style houses around the airport 
?Added the city besides the CKS airport and Sung Shan airport 
?Added ships into the sea 
?Sung Shan airport and its surroundings 
?Taipei freeway 
?Added the landmark of Taipei "Memorial Hall" 
?Added Taipei 101 building 
?Added the landmark of Grand Hotel 
?Added the highway around the Sung Shan Airport 
?Included Kaoshiung International Airport 
?LandClass Textures
